# textdomain: mcl_init
The world has the custom Mineclonia mapgen enabled in combination with mcl_levelgen inhibiting mods. Disable the mods (@1) or update the mcl_singlenode_mapgen setting in @2 to play the world.=
Outdated Client version detected!=Bezero bertsio zaharra detektatu da!
Do not show again=Ez berriro erakutsi
Leave Server=Utzi Zerbitzaria
Ignore=Ez kasurik egin
You are connecting with an unsupported client. This will generally not keep you from playing the game but you should expect some visual issues, particularly with mobs and certain items.@n@nTo enjoy the best mineclonia experience use a minetest/luanti client of version 5.9.0 or greater.=Onartuta ez dagoen bezero batekin konektatzen ari zara. Orokorrean jolastu ahal izan beharko zenuke, baina arazo bisual batzuk ikus ditzakezu, batez ere izaki eta objektu batzuekin.@n@nmineclonia-ren esperientzia hoberenaz gozatzeko, erabili minetest/luanti-ren bezeroaren 5.9.9 bertsioa edo berriagoa.
